ReturnPolicy.Description:
All our Mochila Bags are shipped from United States to any country after your payment is succesfully accepted. 

Free shipping within the United States with USPS priority mail which generally takes 1-3 business days to arrive.  

International shipping: We ship your packages with USPS which generally takes 10-15 business days to arrIve and with International economy shipping may take up to 4 weeks. 

 Wayuu Hands wants client satisfaction. If we make a mistake packing your order, or if the description is materially different than the item you receive, please contact us and we will fix the problem at no additional cost to you. We will accept returns only for faulty or damaged items. Please be sure about the item before purchase. We do not accept any returns if you have changed your mind.

We will issue a refund for what you paid for the item minus shipping fees and a 10% restocking fees. This fee wont be cashed if you are returning an item that was received damaged or defective.

Your mochila bag could have colors slightly different than what you were expecting, this does not qualify as defective, as many different factors affect how the colors shows.
